/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Modern Partition Desi<\/strong>g<strong>ns Between Living-Dining Rooms<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Faux marble laminates as a partition? Yes, these partitions add warmth and texture to a living room, making them a popular choice for modern interiors. They can create a sense of privacy without completely closing off a space, making them ideal for open-plan living areas. Available in various finishes, including natural, stained, and painted, you can find the perfect match for your living room&#8217;s style.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/14171805\/modern-partition-design-between-living-dining.jpg\" alt=\"Modern partition design between the living and dining rooms features faux marble laminates for a textured look\" class=\"wp-image-54917\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/14171805\/modern-partition-design-between-living-dining.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/14171805\/modern-partition-design-between-living-dining-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/14171805\/modern-partition-design-between-living-dining-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/14171805\/modern-partition-design-between-living-dining-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/14171805\/modern-partition-design-between-living-dining-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Gold veins and marble is a fail-proof combination<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get 20% extra space with partition designs in your home\" src=\"https:\